{"parentUuid":"fe077b68-9d15-4bab-8c3e-dcb60523b5ef","isSidechain":false,"message":{"id":"8be212bb-1a83-4e7f-9fc1-e195f7b525af","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about two things:\n1. Why they're getting API errors when using Claude in VS Code\n2. Why all their previous conversations are gone\n\nLet me address both questions directly.\n\nFor the API errors in VS Code - this could be due to several reasons:\n- The model is set to `deepseek-chat` (not a Claude model) - Claude Code typically needs to use Anthropic's Claude models\n- API key configuration issues\n- Network/proxy issues\n\nFor the lost conversations - this could be related to the model switching or session management.\n\nLet me check the current settings to give a more informed answer.","signature":"8be212bb-1a83-4e7f-9fc1-e195f7b525af"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":43898,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":341,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"0236e4d5-7eb6-46e3-9880-ec17e59faade","timestamp":"2026-04-27T08:41:37.357Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"c:\\Users\\Administrator\\Desktop","sessionId":"281dfeaf-95f8-4645-a92d-07a9df200d29","version":"2.1.120","gitBranch":"HEAD"}
{"parentUuid":"0236e4d5-7eb6-46e3-9880-ec17e59faade","isSidechain":false,"message":{"id":"8be212bb-1a83-4e7f-9fc1-e195f7b525af","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我看了一下你的情况，两个问题：\n\n**1. API 错误**\n\n你的模型被切换到了 `deepseek-chat`，这不是 Claude 的原生模型。Claude Code 在 VS Code 扩展中运行时，需要配置正确的 Anthropic API key 才能工作。如果是用第三方 API 代理（中转），可能出现了：\n- API key 过期或无效\n- 中转服务不稳定\n- 模型路由配置不对\n\n**2. 之前的对话都没了**\n\nClaude Code 的对话历史是**会话级别的**，不会永久保存在 VS Code 中。每次关闭窗口、重启扩展、或者切换模型后，之前的会话上下文就会丢失。这是正常行为，不是数据被删了。\n\n---\n\n你能告诉我你用的是：\n- **官方 Anthropic API**，还是**第三方中转/代理 API**？\n- 在 VS Code 中是否设置了 `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY` 环境变量，或者通过 `claude_config.json` 配置的？\n\n这样我可以帮你定位具体原因。"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":43898,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":341,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"22e00fb2-2d07-4a40-9b83-2f8168f93a0c","timestamp":"2026-04-27T08:41:41.535Z","userType":"external","entrypoint":"claude-vscode","cwd":"c:\\Users\\Administrator\\Desktop","sessionId":"281dfeaf-95f8-4645-a92d-07a9df200d29","version":"2.1.120","gitBranch":"HEAD"}
